	   <div class="comcontent" style="display:block;" id="comcontent_570621">
		<p class="comment_body">I also tend to avoid apps with nagging advertisement, although in the latest Android versions it's become less of an issue since you can now select which apps can show messages in the notification bar. <br />
 <br />
It was annoying when you would unlock your phone after hearing a notification sound only to find that (eg) GunBros was letting you know that there were some "awesome" deals on in-app purchases. <br />
 <br />
I'm not getting any of those kind of notifications now (and haven't for a long time) although I'm not sure if that's only because of said blocking feature or because I'm more carefully choosing what apps I install.</p>
